    "description_long": "This is a cylindrical, upright fire hydrant with a robust metallic body painted in a weathered blue color. The hydrant features a central vertical column with a domed top, flanked by two large hose connection outlets on either side and a smaller outlet facing forward. Each outlet is capped, and the side caps are secured with short chains. The base is square and appears bolted to the ground, indicating a fixed installation. The surface shows signs of wear and exposure, with some discoloration and minor rust, typical of outdoor urban infrastructure.",
